			"value": "<p><em>Staff, Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p>This staff can be wielded as a magic Quarterstaff that grants a +2 bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls made with it. It also has the following additional properties. Once one of these properties is used, it can't be used again until the next dawn.</p><p><strong>Activation</strong></p><ul><li><p>While holding the staff, you can do one of the following abilities.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Lightning</strong><br /><br />No Action - 1/Dawn<br /><em>Trigger: When you hit with a melee attack using the staff</em></p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> [[/damage 2d6 Lightning]] damage.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Thunder<br /></strong><br />No Action - 1 Round - 1/Dawn<br /><em>Trigger: When you hit with a melee attack using the staff<br /></em><strong>[[/save CON 17]]{Constitution Save (DC 17)}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[Stunned] until the end of your next turn.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success: </strong>No effect.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Thunder and Lightning<br /><br />Bonus Action</strong> - 1/Dawn<br /><em>Trigger: When you hit with a melee attack using the staff<br /></em>Use Lightning and Thunder properties at the same time.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lightning Strike<br />Action</strong> - 120 ft. Long 5 ft. Wide - 1/Dawn<br /><strong>[[/save DEX 17]]{Dexterity Save (DC 17)}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage 9d6 Lightning]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success: </strong>Half damage.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Thunderclap<br /></strong><br /><strong>Action</strong> - 60 ft. Emenation (Self) - 1 Minute - 1/Dawn</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage  2d6 Thunder]] damage and &amp;reference[Deafened].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half Damage</p></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>",
